        <div class="section_header_text">
            <h2 class="home-bestselling-header">ABOUT US</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-about-us-bodytext mb-3 mt-3">
        <div class="row mt-2">
            <div class="col-md-2 mx-auto about-us-img-div">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/bukola-profile.jpg" class="mx-auto"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10 about-us-text">
                Hi, my name is Bukola. I am the owner of houseofdqueens; an african fashion industry that offers quality and exclusive african print fabrics, we also have collections of african inspired fashion accessories and african made clothing(ready to wear and custom made)
                <br />
